subject: Australian Open (Tennis)
Tennis
lead_paragraph: Roger Federer dispatched Bernard Tomic in straight sets Saturday in their third round match at the Australian Open. Kimiko Date-Krumm, 42, lost to the 21-year-old Bojana Jovanovski.
